text.tspan: あなた自身を快適にさせなさい

flowRoot.flowPara: Ubuntu is available in many different languages. Take a look at the Language Support administration and choose whichever translations you need. Then you can choose a language before logging in and we will try our best to speak it.

Ubuntu's translations are contributed by generous users. If you notice any errors or omissions, feel free to help out at translations.launchpad.net. Many applications have a "Translate this application" option in their Help menu.
